description:
City life and versatility are quite the pair, and these adidas shoes give them both a starring role. Inspired by designs built for an active lifestyle, they offer a modern take on best-in-class comfort and style. The neoprene collar and mesh upper are key for breathability, while the BOOST midsole meets your every step with energy and support. It all comes together on a rubber outsole that gives you traction whenever you need it.
Made with a series of recycled materials, this upper features at least 50% recycled content. This product represents just one of our solutions to help end plastic waste.

description: What makes the adidas Forum shoes so iconic? Let's count the ways: the X-detail, ankle strap, layered upper and padded tongue. It's all about OG '80s hardwood style. These adidas shoes celebrate European basketball with inspired colors and a vintage looking graphic placement. With their adjustable hook-and-loop straps and a synthetic leather upper, they're tailored for all day comfort and indisputable style.
title: Forum 84 High Shoes

description: The adidas Trailcross range was built from the ground up with adventurous mountain biking in mind. The Five Ten Trailcross LT mountain bike shoes deliver, with a lightweight feel that's comfortable on and off the bike. The breathable mesh upper makes for quick-drying comfort, so you're always ready to keep riding. A Stealth Phantom rubber outsole and Dotty tread provide precise pedal control, while added tread features at the toe and heel make for confident footing when exploring off the bike. A reinforced toe box adds peace of mind when pedaling in rough terrain, and the cushioned midsole delivers all-day comfort on or off the bike. When your ride plans include a little of everything, the Trailcross LT has the versatility to get adventurous.
title: Adistar Cushion Shoes
